---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sleep Issues" description="Struggling with sleep? MBS Medical can help identify what's behind your restless nights and build a care plan that works. Telehealth across Florida.">

  <section class="pt-40 pb-28 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="max-w-xl">
          <span class="label text-accent block mb-5">Sleep Issues</span>
          <h1 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.0] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text mb-8">
            Restless nights<br />shouldn't run <em class="text-accent italic">your life</em>
          </h1>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
            When you can't get quality sleep, everything suffers — your energy, your focus, your mood, and your health. We take the time to understand what's behind your sleep issues and build a plan that actually works.
          </p>
          <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center font-ui text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] bg-primary text-bg border border-primary px-7 py-3 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300">Book a Visit</a>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
          <img src="/images/sleep.jpg" alt="Struggling with sleep" class="w-full h-auto rounded-2xl" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What We Address -->
  <section class="pb-28 sm:pb-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-accent block mb-5">What We Address</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">More than just <em class="text-accent italic">tired</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Difficulty Falling Asleep</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Racing thoughts, restlessness, or an inability to wind down — we'll evaluate what's keeping you up and explore treatment options tailored to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Waking Through the Night</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">Frequent wake-ups, difficulty staying asleep, or waking up too early. We look at the full picture — medications, conditions, habits — to find the root cause.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Daytime Exhaustion</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-sm leading-relaxed">When poor sleep bleeds into your days — brain fog, fatigue, irritability, and crashing in the afternoon. We'll help you break the cycle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Our Approach -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-accent block mb-5">Our Approach</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">Finding what's <em class="text-accent italic">really</em> going on</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-4xl">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-3">Comprehensive Evaluation</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed">We start by understanding your full health picture — sleep patterns, medical history, current medications, stress levels, and lifestyle factors that could be contributing to your sleep issues.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-3">Personalized Treatment</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed">Based on your evaluation, we'll build a care plan that may include medication management, behavioral strategies, lab work to rule out underlying conditions, or referrals when needed.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-3">Ongoing Monitoring</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed">Sleep issues rarely resolve overnight. We follow up, adjust your plan as needed, and make sure you're actually seeing improvement — not just managing symptoms.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-3">Connected Care</h3>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed">If your sleep issues are connected to other conditions we manage — like weight, hormones, or chronic health issues — we address them together as part of your whole care plan.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-accent pl-8 sm:pl-10">
          <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">Ready to finally<br /><em class="text-accent italic">sleep</em> again?</h2>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-[480px]">Book a visit and talk to a provider who'll take the time to figure out what's going on — and help you get the rest you deserve.</p>
          <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center font-ui text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] bg-primary text-bg border border-primary px-7 py-3 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300">Book a Visit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach((e) => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); }); }, { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>
